defs.name: CString
defs.docs:
A type representing an owned, C-compatible, nul-terminated string with no nul bytes in the
 middle.

defs.name: CStr
defs.docs: Representation of a borrowed C string.

defs.name: NulError
defs.docs: An error indicating that an interior nul byte was found.

defs.name: FromBytesWithNulError
defs.docs: An error indicating that a nul byte was not in the expected position.

defs.name: IntoStringError
defs.docs: An error indicating invalid UTF-8 when converting a [`CString`] into a [`String`].

defs.name: log2
defs.docs: the log base 2 of an integer value

defs.name: round_up_power_of_two
defs.docs:
rounds the given `value` to the nearest base,
 which must be a power of two
